      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg p-2 ms-6 me-6 mt-4 bg-red-100 hover:bg-red-200 text-red-800 font-medium">
      <a href="">
        <p class="text-center">Có 1 deadline đến sắp đến hạn</p>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg p-2 ms-6 me-6 mt-4 bg-red-100 hover:bg-red-200 text-red-800 font-medium">
